{| class="infobox bordered" style="width:250px" |+ '''South Korea–Japan''' |- |colspan="2" style="text-align:center" | [[Image:Japan North Korea South Korea Locator.png|250px]] |- style="height:0.6em" | style="background:#3c9d3c;" | | style="background:#FF4040; | |- | scope=col style="width:50%; text-align:center"| {{flagbig|1=South Korea|size=50x45px}} | scope=col style="width:50%; text-align:center"| {{flagbig|1=Japan|size=50x45px}} |}
Because of their proximity and similar sporting cultures, [[South Korea]] and [[Japan]] are frequent rivals in a wide variety of international sports.
