'''John D. Eyles''' (born 1946) is a Canadian geographer, having been a Distinguished University Professor at [[McMaster University]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mcmaster.ca/univsec/reports_lists/DistUnivProf.pdf |title=University Distinguished Professors |publisher=mcmaster.ca |accessdate=January 28, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.science.mcmaster.ca/geo/people/faculty/eyles_j/index.html |title=John D. Eyles |publisher=mcmaster.ca |accessdate=January 28, 2017}}</ref> In 2001, he was elected fellow of the [[Royal Society of Canada]].

