===Camp, 2011===
[[Bill Luxton]], MLA for [[Camp (constituency)|Camp]], resigned from the Legislative Assembly on 4 November 2011 due to his prologued absence from the Falklands, which was increasing the workload of the other MLAs.<ref>{{cite news |title=Camp representative Bill Luxton steps down from Falklands’ Legislative Assembly |author= |url=http://en.mercopress.com/2011/11/04/camp-representative-bill-luxton-steps-down-from-falklands-legislative-assembly |newspaper=[[MercoPress]] |date=4 November 2011 |accessdate=28 December 2013}}</ref> The seat was filled by [[Ian Hansen]], who was the only candidate when nominations closed on 30 November 2011.
