== ''kritisk etnografi'' == {{Infobox journal | title = kritisk etnografi | cover = | editor = Sten Hagberg, Jörgen Hellman | discipline = [[Ethnography]], [[social anthropology]], [[cultural anthropology]] | former_names = | abbreviation = kritisk etnografi | publisher = Swedish Society for Anthropology and Geography | country = Sweden | frequency = Biannual | history = 2018–present | openaccess = Yes | license = | impact = | impact-year = | website = http://kritisketnografi.se | link1 = http://kritisketnografi.se/issues | link1-name = Online access | ISSN = | eISSN = 2003-1173 | OCLC = | LCCN = | italic title=no }} '''''kritisk etnografi – Swedish Journal of Anthropology''''' is a biannual [[peer-reviewed]] [[open access]] [[academic journal]] covering the field of [[ethnography]]. It was established in 2018 and is published by the Swedish Society for Anthropology and Geography. The first part of the journal name, ''kritisk etnografi'' (critical ethnography) is in [[Swedish language|Swedish]]. The [[editors-in-chief]] are Sten Hagberg ([[Uppsala University]]) and Jörgen Hellman ([[University of Gothenburg]]).
